{"title": "Post-logon activity", "type": "markdown", "aggs": [], "params": {"fontSize": 12, "openLinksInNewTab": true, "markdown": "### 🖥️ Post-logon activity
What accounts did after logging in. **Windows:** top users / images aggregate Sysmon Event 1; the **Windows session activity** table at the very bottom carries full command lines (a column, not aggregated) — filter it by `logonId` to scope to one RDP session. PowerShell script paths follow.

